title: Jillian and Bob on the radio!
description:
They have a whole lot of fun and share a whole lot of knowledge.  Out of the shoot it's all about child obesity.  Some awesome, solid advice. Then both Jillian and Bob talk to callers and guide them through their questions on diet, fitness and overall wellness.  A real cool breakthrough happens here.
